         <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p>In this grave lies the body, Rull[- . .. ], of good memory, [dear to our heart], who was killed by an irresistible sword. He lived in peace for more or less 35 years; 
               he left this world on day 6 of the month of December, indiction 13. Amen. </p>
